334
00:16:52,560 --> 00:16:54,560
[untuk memindahkan
kakitangan jabatan yang lain.]

335
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,920
Sepanjang masa peperiksaan berlangsung
di Akademi Hongwen,

336
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,960
sekiranya sesuatu hal
berkaitan dengan pengaturan keselamatan,

337
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,520
[awak boleh memindahkan kakitangan]

338
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:03,000
di merata tempat ikut kehendak awak.

339
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:06,600
Patik junjung kasih Yang Amat Berbahagia.

340
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:17,320
Yang Mulia.

341
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:19,680
Bendahara Zhang telah
merampas Akademi Hongwen.

342
00:17:21,120 --> 00:17:21,920
Orang tua yang licik!

343
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,240
Dia mendahului saya lagi.

344
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:33,840
Memang seronok.

345
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:41,600
Yang Mulia.

346
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:43,150
Cikgu.

347
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,150
Tepat masanya awak datang.

348
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:46,280
Tengok, adakah dahlia kuning diraja ini

349
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:47,150
cantik berkembang?

350
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:48,840
Cantik sekali!

351
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,000
[Yang Mulia.]

352
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,400
[Kali ini, Maharani Balu]

353
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:54,240
mempercayakan peperiksaan Akademi Hongwen

354
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,720
kepada patik.

355
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:57,240
[Pelajar-pelajar Akademi Hongwen]

356
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:58,920
[paling cemerlang dalam
kalangan pelajar di negara ini.]

