00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:13,400
[lagi meriah suasananya?]

397
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,960
Yang Mulia.

398
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:17,800
Adakah kita patut tolong dia?

399
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:22,800
Apa yang awak cakap tadi?

