00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:54,360
[Ketua Shen.]

402
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,120
[Tanggungjawab peperiksaan Akademi Hongwen]

403
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:57,600
[tetap telah diserahkan
