00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:10,520
[Dalam tempoh peperiksaan
berlangsung di Akademi Hongwen,]

411
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,200
Raja Ying, Raja Xian,

412
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,360
Bendahara Zhang dan Lai Luozhi

413
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,840
pasti bertindak.

414
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:15,880
Awasi mereka dengan ketat.

