00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:18,960
Pengaturan keselamatan berdekat
dengan Akademi Hongwen

417
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:19,920
mesti dipandang berat,

418
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:20,640
boleh suruh

419
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,240
pengawal istana dan mata-mata membantu.

